snippet.title: 72 HOORAIN Official Trailer
snippet.description:
"72 Hoorain" is a tale, where conviction merges with chaos, where belief dances with brutality, and where the unimaginable becomes a haunting reality. Prepare to be swept away by "72 Hoorain," a gripping tale that delves into the depths of the human psyche and explores the twisted paths taken by Fidayeens. In this riveting narrative, an unfathomable force is unleashed, driven by a belief so fierce that it defies all logic. These Fidayeens, bound by an unyielding faith, embark on a harrowing journey that leads them to the celestial realms. Their ultimate goal? To meet the legendary 72 Virgins, known as the Hoorain.

snippet.title: Tere Bin 2nd Last Ep - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin 2nd Last Episode - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Last Episode Teaser - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

7:11 PM Trailer Telugu on Mythri Movie Makers.

Here's the 7:11 PM Theatrical Trailer that gives you a surreal experience of a race against time. Some extraterrestrial humans travel through space, a loving pair that are inseparable even by destiny and some greedy goons whose fate is reversed by time. Hold your devices, Sit back, Relax & Enjoy..!

#711PM #SaahasPagadala #DeepikaReddy #TessWalsh #ChaituMadala #MythriMovieMakers #ArcusFilms #711PMTRAILER #711PMMOVIE

Episode 3809: Jethalal Ne Baati Mithaiyaan
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena returns from their expedition, and Champaklal compliments them on their environmentally friendly driving. Tapu informs Champaklal that Bhide has praised their troop's initiative. Jetha delivers candy to the children and also informs them about his confirmed dealership. Tapu congratulates his father on a fantastic haul. Taarak sneaks into the kitchen to take some sweets, but Anjali apprehends him. Later, Jetha offers Anjali and Taarak treats as well. Will Anjali let Taarak eat, or will she frown?

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. 3. Je dil thoda kre hoje dharti v sona, tuc jithe jithe perr dhar do, dil thoda kre  ik takni de naal tuc mausaman nu change krdon, ji oho thonu pyar de sunehe kll da, jihde kehne vich hi hun smaa chalda, te gaddi de brakean naal america thalde, Area bathinda Goniana vall de.

"HOOK REPEAT"

4. MAAN MAAN MAAN MAAN kahi jaane ho, saade tuc kehne vich rhi jane ho, kde kde gussa kde pyar bolda, sahi jane ho ji tuc sahi jane ho, Ji jaan jaan munda thode naal turda, hassa jive paani ch patasa ghurde, lifetime thode naal hi naah judd da, rishta sharab naal jive gudd de.
"HOOK REPEAT"

snippet.title: Affair With Office HR  | PART 2 | FT. Purav Jha, Rashmeet Kaur | Hasley India Originals!
snippet.description:
A relationship works only if both the partners put equal efforts in it. Chahe wo ladka ho ya ladki, dono ko hi equal understanding ki zarurat hoti hai!
But there are times when life throws such challenges where despite of all the efforts and understanding, things don‚Äôt work out. Ab chahe use misunderstanding kehlo ya phir carelessness!
Toh kuch aisa hi hua jab Aayush ne Shraddha ka office join kiya and he starts working as a junior to her.
Kuch misunderstandings hui aur kuch logo ne uthaya uska galat fayda! 
Ab kya hua, kaise hua, kab hua, in questions ke answers aapko milenge second episode Mei!

So don‚Äôt miss out on this amazing story and watch the episode till the end!

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Uniform Civil Code Explained: ‡§á‡§§‡§®‡•Ä ‡§π‡§æ‡§Ø ‡§§‡•å‡§¨‡§æ ‡§ï‡•ç‡§Ø‡•ã‡§Ç? | UCC | PM Modi | Indian Democracy | RJ Raunak
snippet.description:
Hours after Prime Minister Narendra Modi advocated for the nationwide implementation of the Uniform Civil Code (UCC), the All India Muslim Personal Law Board held an emergency online meeting late on Tuesday evening. During the meeting, the Islamic personal law body decided to oppose the proposed law, which seeks to formulate and implement a set of common personal laws for all the citizens of India regardless of their religion, caste, and creed.

During the online meeting attended by AIMPLB president Saifullah Rehmani; Maulana Khalid Rasheed Farangi Mahali, chairman of Islamic Centre of India and member of AIMPLB; AIMPLB lawyers; and among others -- the Muslim body agreed on presenting its views more powerfully in front of the Law Commission. At the meeting, the documents to be submitted to the Law Commision were also finalised.

In this video we'll talk about UCC and what difference it would bring into Indian Society. What was the history and how this code will be a historic decision?

Like the video and please Subscribe.

snippet.title: NALLI BIRYANI | Mutton Biryani Recipe Cooking in Village | Mutton Bone Marrow | Lamb Shanks Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook the Nalli biryani recipe using fresh lamb shanks. We use Seeraga samba rice to make this traditional biryani recipe. The special of this mutton recipe is while eating biryani, and we taste a lot of bone marrow with the meat.

We enjoy the biryani at the evening! The taste is delicious!

snippet.description:

Episode 3808: Jethalal Ke Priya Mitra
--------------------------------------------------------
The client finally meets with Jetha and Taarak, but Champaklal comes and unintentionally reveals the truth. The client is unhappy because Jethalal has been lying so far. Champaklal assures the clients that his son is innocent and that he never intended to conceal the truth. Jetha admits that he tried to avoid the encounter due to his poor command of the English language. The clients agreed to the terms after being impressed by Jetha's regard for his father. Taarak informs Jetha that he has come to assist Anjali at her request. Jetha later arranges an intimate dining experience for Taarak and his wife as an acknowledgment.

---------------------
The Nawab of Murshidabad is depressed, so he asks his montri to find a means to make him feel better. Gopal's wife creates a sweet treat called "Taler Bora" (sweet fritters). Will this sweet dish cheer up the Nawab?

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

snippet.title: J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding
snippet.description:
J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding 

" " United by Love " is a documentary focused on our journey from starting out as friends and aspiring actors, to falling in love and making it big through YouTube and finally getting married to each other. We come from southern part of India and we feel lucky to have a successful relationship even though our families follow different religions. We personally thank "Enchanteur", a brand centered around romance & love, joining hands with us in celebrating our love and making it special . Riding towards more adventure in our life and career, we pause for a moment and share these precious moments with you all. 

Love always, 

J& V

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
